item.title: Mother’s Day with ‘Top Chef’ Padma Lakshmi
item.description: Today, we sit with writer and television host Padma Lakshmi! At the top, we discuss the return of her Hulu docuseries Taste the Nation (6:40), a formative episode in El Paso, Texas (10:14), and how the show is guided by Padma’s personal history (13:59). Then, she reflects on her childhood in New York City (16:07), a heartbreaking event that brought her back to India (19:05*), and her unexpected entry to the modeling industry (27:14)...
